  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a 3-month pilot study of 10 adolescents with chronic daily headache. Teens will be
      placed on a modified Atkins diet and followed with 2 subsequent visits to assess for
      headache improvement.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients are placed on the diet and followed with various measures for 3 months. If the diet
      is helpful it is continued. Patients are still being enrolled as of 9/6/06.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
